are doing online, as opposed

00:56:09.960 --> 00:56:12.580
to, I wouldn't let them
just do anything online.

00:56:12.580 --> 00:56:15.000
I would do that.

00:56:15.000 --> 00:56:17.760
People also ask me what did I
do to make them so independent?

00:56:17.760 --> 00:56:20.650
Boy they are really independent.

00:56:20.650 --> 00:56:23.610
And I think the main thing
I did is, I didn't have

00:56:23.610 --> 00:56:25.230
any help when they were small.

00:56:25.230 --> 00:56:27.970
It was just like me
and the three kids.

00:56:27.970 --> 00:56:32.490
And my husband is a high energy
physicist, professor of physics

00:56:32.490 --> 00:56:36.290
and his main interest
in life is particles.

00:56:36.290 --> 00:56:38.730
